Museums

Rijksmuseum (Amsterdam)

Google Maps
1hr 40min
1hr 8min
Link

The most famous museum in the Netherlands and it is huge and has a wild variety of different objects and paintings. Home of many paintings you will actually recognize most notably by Rembrandt and Vermeer. But theres an antique gun collection and armor and you could spend days here. Right next to the Van Gogh Museum so its good to combine the two.

Google Maps

A museum with painting by a lot of famous painters right in the middle of the beautiful national park. The museum itself is modern and has a lot of windows so it makes you feel like youre right in the forest (which you are).
